It would be quite useful if, instead of line-by-line output of the processing happening in instance generation (which becomes very hard to follow), Walbottle outputted the following debug information at a high level:

Timings:
 • $schema_hash generation took x seconds
 • $schema_hash validation took y seconds
 • $schema_hash application took z seconds
 • $schema_hash2 generation took s seconds
 • …

Schemas:
 • $schema_hash:
     { some schema }
   Found at:
    - $['json']['path']
    - $['json']['path2']
 • $schema_hash2:
     { some other schema }
   Found at:
    - …
